<h2 class="bold font-l">"You can't make me talk!"</h2>
<p class="_pmvv-vidbox-descTxt">
Barbie hits Ken where it hurts to get the information she needs. </p>
</div>
<div class="video-examples-thumbs">
<a href="#video-link" data-video-id="465cgq" data-video-descrip="Gumball, Darwin, and Richard interrogate Larry by doing unspeakable things to Burgie the Joyful Burger mascot." data-video-title="The Menu" data-video-url="https://d1w6li7s85ibls.cloudfront.net/qvbr/465cgq_640x360p_qvbr.mp4" data-video-thumbnail="https://static.tvtropes.org/trope_videos_transcoded/images/sd/465cgq.jpg" data-video-trope="Main/InterrogationByVandalism" data-video-tropename="Interrogation by Vandalism" data-video-approval="APPROVED" data-video-troper-rating="" data-video-average-rating="" data-video-rating-count="" data-video-media-sources="WesternAnimation/TheAmazingWorldOfGumball" class="video-launch-link video-overlay-link video-background-image lazy-image" data-src="https://static.tvtropes.org/trope_videos_transcoded/images/sd/465cgq.jpg">
